dct_title_s: Bublr Bike Stations Milwaukee County, Wisconsin March 2018
dct_description_sm: This point layer represents Bublr Bikeshare Stations for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2018. The data was obtained from Bublr as an excel worksheet with addresses, latitude and longitude, and stall count information. A shapefile was created by American Geogrphical Society Library Staff.
dct_creator_sm: James Davies (Senior Director of Operations and Planning, Bublr Bikes)
